R -> circumradius
r = inradius
r1, r2, r3 = exradius
* sine rule
sinA/a = sinB/b = sinC/c = 1/2R = 2(area)/abc
* cosine rule
cosA = (b^2+c^2-a^2)/2bc
..
* sin(A/2) = sqrt((s-b)(s-c)/bc)
  cos(A/2) = sqrt(s(s-a)/bc)
* a = bcosC+ccosB
* r = area/s
* 2r<=R
* r1+r2+r3 = 4R+r
  r1 = area/(s-a) = stan(A/2) = 4Rsin(A/2)cos(B/2)cos(C/2)
  r1r2+r2r3+r3r1 = s^2 = r1r2r3/r
* r+2R = s in right traingle
